# Gitleaks Ignore patterns (Fixed Path Matching)
# These patterns match files processed during 'gitleaks detect'

# Build and Vendor Noise
**/node_modules/**
**/dist/**
**/dev-dist/**
**/.wrangler/**
**/.codeql/**
**/.security/bin/**

# Lock files
package-lock.json

# Secret/Env Files
**/.actrc**
**/.secrets**
**/.env**
**/.dev.vars**
**/.demo.vars**
**/.event**

# External WASM/Binary
**/*.wasm**
**/*.map**